children.content: ROADMAP CIAM LMFR - STEP 1 - Reach5 is deployed instead of WAC - WAC is removed - WALT ensure backword compatibility - Bi-directional synchronization between R5 & REFCLI is ensured by MDM
Internal synchronization between SCR & MDM is reliable because of asynchronous communication using MDM Kafka bus
REFCLI update is made asynchronously with webhook
WALT offers the same API than WAC but calls R5
CIAM send messages to MDM Kafka bus and no more SCR Active MQ bus
